Missing: Native integrations for major Cloud Providers (AWS CloudWatch, Azure, GCP), Ticketing Systems (Jira, ServiceNow, Zendesk), and other observability tools (New Relic, Dynatrace, Prometheus, Grafana, Splunk).
Industry Standard: 700+ integrations.
Current State: Supports Sentry, Slack, PagerDuty, Opsgenie, Datadog, Teams, Discord.
ğŸ”¥ 3. Incident Management Lifecycle
Missing:
War Rooms: Automatic creation of Zoom bridges or Slack channels dedicated to an incident.
Post-Mortems: Automated generation of incident timelines and post-mortem documents.
Status Pages: Public or private status pages to communicate downtime (e.g., statuspage.io integration).
Incident Roles: Explicit roles like "Incident Commander", "Scribe", "Liaison".
Current State: Basic Alert Grouping and Resolution.
